OL,3,CSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,6,GA trawl for volunteers for redundancy
OL,7,Gat STV was due to close on Friday.
OL,9,FThe firm is planning to cut about 60
OL,10,Fjobs including around 30 in news.
OL,12,FThe main cut the company is planning
OL,13,Fis, of course, the end of the news
OL,14,Fservice for the former Grampian region.
OL,16,FBut it will be several weeks ` maybe
OL,17,Fmonths ` before Ofcom decides whether
OL,18,Fto allow this.
