OL,3,CSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,6,FI'm not quite sure how any broadcaster
OL,7,Fcan reorganise its operations ` or
OL,8,Fdecide whether it can make significant
OL,9,Fnumbers of news staff redundant `
OL,10,Fbefore it knows whether it will
OL,11,Factually be able to make changes to
OL,12,Foutput.
OL,14,FClearly it is possible Ofcom might
OL,15,Fblock the scheme completely, although
OL,16,Fthis is thought highly unlikely.
OL,18,FStill it could insist on a separate
OL,19,Fnews service for the former Grampian
OL,20,Fregion remaining. Stranger things have
OL,21,Fhappened.
