OL,3,CSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,6,FThis clearly would mean keeping a
OL,7,Flarge editorial operation in Aberdeen
OL,8,Fand the north of Scotland.
OL,10,FStudio presentation and production can
OL,11,Fmove to Glasgow without Ofcom
OL,12,Fpermission.
OL,14,FRealistically, if any dedicated output
OL,15,Ffor the north remained it would have
OL,16,Fto be recorded.
OL,18,FMy own suspicion is that Ofcom will
OL,19,Feither approve STV's proposals `
OL,20,Fdespite huge political objections ` or
OL,21,Finsist on a sub-opt for the north.
OL,22,FEven doing this could still save jobs.
