OL,3,CSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,6,FIt is important to remember that STV's
OL,7,Fcurrent service includes both Scottish
OL,8,Fnational news and stories of local and
OL,9,Fregional interest.
OL,11,FAll the news programmes in the nations
OL,12,Fare very different editorially to
OL,13,FEnglish regional programmes.
OL,15,FSTV currently has one advantage over
OL,16,Fthe BBC ` it can also cover the kind
OL,17,Fof local and regional stories which
OL,18,Fare unlikely to be seen on Reporting
OL,19,FScotland.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
