OL,3,CSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,6,FBut is it fair to impose an obligation
OL,7,Fon a commercial broadcaster to do
OL,8,Fsomething which the BBC has never done?
OL,10,FThis is not 1961 or even 1993.
OL,12,FOr does the simple fact that ratings
OL,13,Ffor STV North are good mean that
OL,14,Ftaking the axe to the service is a
OL,15,Fhuge misjudgement?
OL,17,FSTV points out that it's legal
OL,18,Fobligations are greater than those of
OL,19,FUTV and ITV Wales.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/8
