OL,3,CSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,6,FAgainst this are two obvious points.
OL,7,FScotland is bigger than Wales or
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland and has always been
OL,9,Fsplit into three channel 3 regions.
OL,11,FAdd on changing consumer behaviour and
OL,12,Fyou can see that there is at least an
OL,13,Fargument ` if not necessarily a
OL,14,Fcompelling case ` for change.
OL,16,FThe actual boundary between STV's two
OL,17,Fregions merely reflects transmitter
OL,18,Fareas. It is not as simple as saying
OL,19,FAberdeen is different to Glasgow.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
