OL,3,CSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,6,FIt is for all those reasons that Ofcom
OL,7,Fmay face big questions if it does not
OL,8,Frun a lengthy, detailed consultation.
OL,10,FUnions and politicians will be
OL,11,Fcritical if Ofcom simply puts a
OL,12,Fproposed change of this magnitude out
OL,13,Fto a short consultation.
OL,15,FMeanwhile you can expect the unions to
OL,16,Fstep up their fight if compulsory
OL,17,Fredundancies look likely.
OL,19,FThis story could prove very
OL,20,Fsignificant over the coming months.
